{"id":"b6dbc607-7a91-42bc-a592-42ba38545851","title":"1512: To Lodovico di Lionardo di Buonarrota Simoni","type":"main-list-block","children":[{"id":"237f219a-4bb4-4991-a30b-e039b6da3b8c","type":"standoff-editor-block","text":"From Rome, ... [1512].","standoffProperties":[{"id":"45f195a3-62e5-41e8-9e8e-861686e0095b","type":"codex/entity-reference","start":5,"end":8,"value":"501a8a32-2c8a-4934-9060-8c7e36339f0f","zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]},{"id":"16b5931c-b072-427f-b8b9-e1e3c14f649b","type":"codex/time-reference","start":16,"end":19,"value":"5638356a-7600-4857-b10d-e482bd59c841","zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]}],"blockProperties":[]},{"id":"da3a3913-ef42-4af8-b96b-6879e7336abb","type":"standoff-editor-block","text":"To Lodovico di Lionardo di Buonarrota Simoni,","standoffProperties":[{"id":"ff0dca89-407e-4a94-bc61-ec3040ca7872","type":"style/italics","start":0,"end":43,"value":null,"zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]},{"id":"934475c1-2fc2-4c39-a40b-d2e4cc47cbcd","type":"codex/entity-reference","start":3,"end":43,"value":"21671569-3eea-412b-85cc-08f659f58019","zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]}],"blockProperties":[]},{"id":"0a8556e1-b98e-4207-9351-9a9daa2c8086","type":"standoff-editor-block","text":"in Florence.","standoffProperties":[{"id":"daf9c927-2d61-4d77-96f6-b697ee297e58","type":"codex/entity-reference","start":3,"end":10,"value":"671ee7e7-ae1b-4a5a-9591-b40203d5108f","zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]}],"blockProperties":[]},{"id":"5052207e-cc35-4f37-9446-950c51ef1f2f","type":"standoff-editor-block","text":"Dearest Father,\u00A0\u2014\u00A0I sent on to you the information I had gleaned here, and told you what I had heard:\u00A0that is to say, that it was rather a risky affair than otherwise\u00A0\u2014\u00A0that farm near Prato, I mean. However, you are on the spot and can see and find out\u00A0things better than I can here. Act as you think best. As to the letter of authorisation you wish me to send to the Spedalingo, treat me as though I were he and write out exactly what I am to say, with\u00A0the name and address and all. I will make a copy of it and send it to him, for I neither know his name nor how to compose the letter myself. Have no fear about it, for if you buy this land and the Spedalingo should refuse to give you the money, I will come to Florence in person and compel him to\u00A0give it up. If you decide to buy, do not buy\u00A0land near the Arno or another dangerous river: give the preference to what the Spedalingo may\u00A0offer you, and if you can get it for a reasonable price settle the matter. Even if the price were a\u00A0trifle high I should be inclined to take it. I have no occasion to say more. We have not as yet seen any\u00A0sign here of the danger you suspect in Florence,\u00A0and God grant that nothing may happen.","standoffProperties":[{"id":"e831c231-2e21-4d2a-8ea4-5f31597aa9b8","type":"tei/textstructure/salute","start":0,"end":13,"value":null,"zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]},{"id":"f106e93a-8332-4713-94fd-4e31e21c842d","type":"tei/textstructure/opener","start":0,"end":15,"value":null,"zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]},{"id":"9e0e3704-e411-4b62-8881-ff3f4d509b8c","type":"codex/entity-reference","start":0,"end":13,"value":"21671569-3eea-412b-85cc-08f659f58019","zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]},{"id":"56607796-8b15-446f-b6ad-443b7e1f5445","type":"codex/entity-reference","start":18,"end":18,"value":"add92e01-cefe-4f13-94dd-f00eb82155b0","zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]},{"id":"bc64c09b-9e02-4d3d-8008-08f10a53592d","type":"codex/entity-reference","start":31,"end":33,"value":"21671569-3eea-412b-85cc-08f659f58019","zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]},{"id":"df3fde1b-7b41-42ef-863a-408df5cb687e","type":"codex/entity-reference","start":51,"end":51,"value":"add92e01-cefe-4f13-94dd-f00eb82155b0","zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]},{"id":"89fe31da-3365-4470-bfac-391a0a03ff3d","type":"codex/entity-reference","start":80,"end":82,"value":"21671569-3eea-412b-85cc-08f659f58019","zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]},{"id":"873bbc